      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLOSSOMING FUN (3) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Fashion Square (22.93) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. The form out of her last race has been franked. Can find winning form. CHI CHI DOLL (2) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 6th and beaten 7 lengths at this track (23.16). Likely to be about the money. MAXIMUM HUGHES (1) finds it hard to break through. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (22.94) at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Has performed well from this box with a win and six minor placings to her name from 11 starts. Winning chance. CLIFF THE BOSS (5) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can bounce back.",
